            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Patric</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Martialis et <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Patric</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Marcus <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Ling</abbr><ex>ones</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fratr</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>omnib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>offic</abbr><ex>iis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>civilib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> in civi<lb break="no" n="3"/>tate sua <expan><abbr>funct</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> cellam vestibulam e regio<lb break="no" n="4"/>ne columnae cum suis <expan><abbr>omnib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>commod</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ua</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ecunia</ex></expan> vi&amp;lt;c=K&amp;gt;<expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Vertillensib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> largiti sunt 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Schriftfeld in tabula ansata; blattförmige Hedera am Ende der Inschrift. Z. 1: ET-Ligatur; Z. 3: TE-Ligatur; Z. 5: EN-Ligatur. (B): Le Bohec; Provost: Z. 1: et (Lucius)</p>
            </div>
